trans-unit.source: Specifies the source for <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ComboBox"></xref> and <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TextBox"></xref> automatic completion functionality.
Specifies the equivalent of <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.AutoCompleteSource.FileSystem"></xref> and <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.AutoCompleteSource.AllUrl"></xref> as the source.
This is the default value when <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.AutoCompleteMode"></xref> has been set to a value other than the default.
Specifies the equivalent of <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.AutoCompleteSource.HistoryList"></xref> and <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.AutoCompleteSource.RecentlyUsedList"></xref> as the source.
Specifies strings from a built-in <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.AutoCompleteStringCollection"></xref> as the source.
Specifies the file system as the source.
Specifies that only directory names and not file names will be automatically completed.
Includes the Uniform Resource Locators (URLs) in the history list.
Specifies that the items of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ComboBox"></xref> represent the source.
Specifies that no <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.AutoCompleteSource"></xref> is currently in use.
This is the default value of <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.AutoCompleteSource"></xref>.
Includes the Uniform Resource Locators (URLs) in the list of those URLs most recently used.
